Title: Relates to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "North Dansville Veterans Memorial Highway"
Summary: Designates all that portion of the state highway system constituting state route sixty-three in the town of North Dansville, county of Livingston, as the "North Dansville Veterans Memorial Highway".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "North Dansville Veterans Memorial Highway"
